---
title: Teriyaki Eggplant & Slaw Tacos with Sesame Fries & Crushed Peanuts
description: Give taco night an Asian twist with the unbeatable combo of melt-in-the-mouth eggplant in teriyaki sauce, crisp slaw tossed with
creamy mayo and a topping of crushed peanuts. For a special finishing touch, sprinkle sesame seeds on the fries before baking!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/teriyaki-eggplant-slaw-tacos-4f55b6b6.jpg
